headline: Patient Capital Management Q2 2025 Commentary
summary: For the second quarter, the S&P 500 gained 10.9%, the Nasdaq 18.0% and the Dow 5.5%. Opportunity Equity Strategy rose 15.3% net of fees. Read more here.
